text: Hallie Kate Eisenberg, born August 2, 1992, is an American actor. She began her acting career in Pepsi commercials beginning in late 1990s. Eisenberg acted in many movies, television programs and commercials starting from the mid 1990s. ==References== Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:Actors from New Jersey Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:People from East Brunswick, New Jersey
